  "texts": [
    "Image tiles can be extracted from slides, processed and stain normalized, and predictions are generated for each tile from a slide.",
    "The final slide-level prediction is the average prediction from all tiles.",
    "Tile-level predictions can be visualized as a heatmap Fig. 55Fig.",
    "5 Real-time predictions and saliency maps from whole-slide images.",
    "Slideflow Studio provides an interface for generating both whole-slide and focal tile predictions."
  ]
